::Prowl::

Prowl's spark speeds up as Iron Raptor presses her lips to his, a surge of 
emotions going throught the bot. He looks at her as she leans away, smiling 
as he hears her answer. His spark was racing at the feel of her body against 
his, his arms holding her even tighter.

"I'm sorry about that," he says a bit jokingly, smiling and kissing her 
again, "I have no excuse to put duty in front of you, milady."

He looks into her optics as he says this, realizing that he was probably 
speaking the truth. He would give up his own life, even the Maximal cause for 
her, his love was that strong! Love fills his optics as he realizes that, 
leaning in to kiss her again.
